       lake and river fishing access, a swimming pool, Trailside Museums and Zoo, hiking, biking
        and cross-country ski trails. The Perkins Memorial Tower atop Bear Mountain affords
        spectacular views of the park, the Hudson Highlands and Harriman State Park.</p>
