    <br>Montauk, NY</h6>
<p class="card-text">On the eastern tip of the South Shore of Long Island, Montauk Point State Park, offers stunning
  views of the Atlantic Ocean where it meets the Block Island Sound. The view is unique, because, when the water
  is calm, visitors can clearly see the "race" of converging tides from the Atlantic and Block Island Sound.
  Visitors can also use the nature trails to hike or cross-country ski, or spend time watching the seals sun on
  the rocks offshore. Block Island can be seen off in the distance.</p>
